*[[Richard III de Bermingham]], [[Anglo-Irish people|Anglo-Irish]] landowner (b. [[1570 in Ireland|1570]])
*[[Peter Martin (STP)]], [[Dominican Order|Dominican]].
*[[Muiris mac Torna Ó Maolconaire]], scribe and poet.

