The '''39th Motorized Infantry Battalion "Dnipro-2"''' is a formation of the [[Ukrainian Ground Forces]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.mil.gov.ua/news/2015/10/19/analiz-illovausk--14354/|title=Аналіз бойових дій в районі Іловайська після вторгнення російських військ 24-29 серпня 2014 року|access-date=2016-08-18}}</ref> It was created first in spring 2014 as 39th [[Territorial defence battalions (Ukraine)|territorial defense battalion]] "Dnipro-2" from volunteers of [[Dnipropetrovsk Oblast|Dnipropetrovsk oblast]].

== History ==
In August 2014 39th territorial defense battalion "Dnipro-2" had participated in [[Battle of Ilovaisk]].<ref name=":0" />

