'''Aquarius Records''' is a [[Croatia]]n record label established in 1995 in [[Zagreb]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aquarius-records.com/onama.php |title=O nama |publisher=Aquarius Records |date= |accessdate=2013-03-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513213114/http://www.aquarius-records.com/onama.php |archivedate=2013-05-13 |df= }}</ref>

Signed artists include [[General Woo]], [[Kinoklub]], [[Kraljevi ulice]], [[Massimo Savić]], [[Tony Cetinski]], [[Šajeta]], [[Viktor Vidović]], [[Tamara Obrovac]], [[Songkillers]], [[Stoka]], [[Nina Badrić]], [[Lea Dekleva]], [[Damir Urban]], [[Cubismo]] and [[Silente]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aquarius-records.com/izvodjaci.php |title=Izvođači |publisher=Aquarius Records |date= |accessdate=2013-03-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513235102/http://www.aquarius-records.com/izvodjaci.php |archivedate=2013-05-13 }}</ref>

