{{Use Indian English|date=October 2018}}
{{Orphan|date=February 2013}}

'''Radio FTII''' is owned and managed by Film and Television Institute of India. Radio FTII broadcasts programs based on social awareness, youth, hygiene and health along with some talk shows of social workers.It is aired on [[FM broadcasting|FM]] 90.4. This radio station can be heard in the city of [[Pune]], [[Maharashtra]] only.

