{{Infobox diocese | jurisdiction = Diocese | name = Vinh | latin = Dioecesis Vinhensis | local = Giáo phận Vinh | image = | image_size = | image_alt = | caption = | coat = <!-- Coat of arms file name (excluding File: prefix) --> | coat_size = | coat_alt = | flag = <!-- Flag file name (excluding File: prefix) --> | flag_size = | flag_alt = <!---- Locations ----> | country = [[Vietnam]] | territory = | province = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Hanoi|Hanoi]] | metropolitan = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Hanoi|Hanoi]] | archdeaconries = | deaneries = | subdivisions = | coordinates = <!-- Use {{coord}} --> <!---- Statistics ----> | area_km2 = 30,594 | area_sqmi = <!-- Area in square miles, automatically converted --> | area_footnotes = | population = 6,155,000 | population_as_of = 2010 | catholics = 492,971 | catholics_percent = 8 | parishes = | churches = <!-- Number of churches in the diocese --> | congregations = <!-- Number of congregations in the diocese --> | schools = <!-- Number of church supported schools in the diocese --> | members = <!-- Number of members in the diocese --> <!---- Information ----> | denomination = [[Roman Catholic]] | sui_iuris_church = [[Latin Church]] | rite = [[Roman Rite]] | established = | cathedral = Cathedral of the Assumption in [[Nghệ An Province]] | cocathedral = | patron = | patron_title = <!-- Use to override the default label "Patron saint" --> | priests = <!-- Number of priests in the diocese --> <!---- Current leadership ----> | pope = {{Incumbent pope}} <!-- DO NOT CHANGE. This will update the Popes Automatically as they change --> | patriarch = | major_archbishop = | bishop = Paul Nguyên Thai Hop | bishop_title = <!-- Type of ordinary: i.e. Bishop or Archbishop. Default is Bishop --> | metro_archbishop = [[Pierre Nguyễn Văn Nhơn]] | coadjutor = | suffragans = <!-- List most senior first (usually reckoned by date of consecration); use | suffragan = for one --> | auxiliary_bishops = Pierre Nguyên Văn Viên | apostolic_admin = | vicar_general = | episcopal_vicar = | archdeacons = <!-- List most senior first (usually reckoned by date of first collation); use | archdeacon = for one--> | emeritus_bishops = Paul-Marie Cao Ðình Thuyên <small>Bishop Emeritus (2000-2010)</small> <!---- Map ----> | map = | map_size = | map_alt = | map_caption = <!---- Website ----> | website = [http://giaophanvinh.net/ Website of the Diocese] | footnotes = }} The '''diocese of Vinh''' ({{lang-la|Dioecesis Vinhensis}}) is a [[Roman Catholic]] diocese in central [[Vietnam]]. Paul-Marie Cao Đình Thuyên became bishop in 2000.
The creation of the diocese in present form was declared November 24, 1960.
The diocese covers an area of 30,783&nbsp;km², and is a [[suffragan diocese]] of the [[Archdiocese of Hanoi]].
By 2004, the diocese of Vinh had about 453,018 believers (7.9% of the population), 126 [[priest]]s and 143 [[parish]]es.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dvinh.html Catholic Hierarchy Directory]</ref>
Assumption Cathedral in Nghi Dien Commune ([[Nghệ An Province]]) has been assigned as the [[Cathedral]] of the [[diocese]].<ref>[http://www.gcatholic.org/churches/data/cathVN.htm#chk GCatholic.org]</ref>
